text:
To those who came to see us perform,
I don't want to leave them disappointed.

I'll give it my all,
and do everything I can right now.

These costumes, they're matching for all 283 of us, aren't they?
It somehow... makes me feel more reassured.

So, it makes me feel like I can
just vaguely think, "I can do this".
It's a strange thing to say, though.
